      "cookedHtml": "<p>I will correct you if you are wrong indeed! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/slight_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>Here is my board with the “Board Footers” inactive:<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/a/4/a43f9043ebd6c36efa91f168ca879b241f528802.png\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/a/4/a43f9043ebd6c36efa91f168ca879b241f528802_2_690x448.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"448\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">842×547 26.8 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>And here it is with the setting <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/gianniskoukounas\">@GiannisKoukounas</a> suggested active:</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/4/c/4ced1bbeee247197e3d23a5f18b90f65ffb75ff9.png\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/4/c/4ced1bbeee247197e3d23a5f18b90f65ffb75ff9_2_587x500.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"587\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">832×708 35.8 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\nI am quite sure 1+2+3+4+5=15 and 6+9=15 (I still subscribe to traditional math where there is an objective answer)<p></p>"
